data.name: cmbManufacturer.ToolTip
data.value:
Start Typing a Manufacturer or select one from the dropdown button. If you do not see your manufacturer you can add a new one by selecting "File", "Add Field", "Manufacturer".
Be sure to refresh selections after adding a new Manufacturer.
